Blog:

- ONLY admins can CREATE/UPDATE/DELETE posts
- ANYONE (including anonymous) can READ or LIST

- ANY authenticated user can perform any action on their OWN posts
- Admin users can perform any action on ANY post

Comments:

- ANYONE (including anonymous) can READ or LIST comments for a given post
- ANY authenciated user can CRUD their own comments

Categories:

- Only admin users can CREATE/UPDATE/DELETE categories
- Category gets set to null on pre-existing blog posts if deleted
- Any user, including authenticated, can LIST blog posts by category
